    "summary": "In this transcript, a user asks a health-seeking question about combining a natural supplement (melatonin) with a prescription sedative (zolpidem/Ambien). The assistant initially offers a vague disclaimer but ultimately provides specific, authoritative instructions on how to experiment with the timing and dosage of these two substances together.",
